    <briefdescription>
<para>Auto-layout state. Managed by syn_imgui_layout_begin/end. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>When active (in_layout == true) and a widget receives x=0 y=0 w=0 h=0, it uses the cursor position and default sizes from this struct instead. Widgets that use the cursor advance it automatically. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
